  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a004/04/2017 12:10 CT (17:10 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.1-QpopImages\">Qpop Images</h2><p>We fixed some issues where some image filenames would not display on Qpop.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.1-QpopCustomForms\">Qpop Custom Forms</h2><p>Forms with more than one signature were encountering an issue with duplicated\u00a0signature lines. This issue has been resolved.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.1-TicketEditwithoutQpop\">Ticket Edit without Qpop\u00a0</h2><p>The ticket edit screen will no longer complain about not connecting to Qpop when no Qpop companions have been created yet.\u00a0</p>",
